vulnerability_details: Like polar bears forced onto land as sea ice disappears, Aput's
  traditional hunting grounds have become open water. His specialized knowledge of
  ice conditions, passed down through seven generations, is now useless. He spends
  days walking the shoreline where solid ice platforms once extended for kilometers,
  finding only thin sheets that crack under footsteps.
